data.title: Wiedeman Funeral Home & Cremation Services, Inc.
data.meta_description: Our funeral homes are established on the foundation of providing every family we are privileged to serve with the best service possible.  We pay close attention to details and fulfill each family's wishes in a caring and professional manner.  We treat your family as if they were part of our own family.
data.text:
Whether you have come to us at a time of great need, to prearrange a funeral or even to explore the available services we offer...for three generations and since 1937, we have served all faiths with professionalism and kindness â€“ and we continue this tradition of service today.

We provide traditional funeral services, cremation services, memorial services and graveside services, celebration of life, local and long distance services. We offer a complete range of services for both pre-need and at-need arrangements and a grief follow-up program.

Rest assured that we are here for you to help you through this difficult time. Along with your family and friends, the staff at Wiedeman Funeral Home & Cremation Services, Inc. continue to have concern for you as you adjust to many changes. Some of these changes may carry you into what seems like unknown, painful, and sometimes frightening territory.

The goal of our website is to assist you throughout the entire funeral planning process. It includes the types of services that we provide, merchandise selections and fees for those items.

It also includes information on available personalization options to create a funeral service one that matches the beliefs, hobbies and interests of your loved one. It also provides resources and assistance after the funeral has concluded.

We, at Wiedeman Funeral Home & Cremation Services, Inc., feel that our services should continue long after the funeral is over. If at any time we an be of any assistance, please contact any member of our staff or email us at mail@wiedemanfh.com. Yesterday, Today & Tomorrow, We are here for You.
